>>>>>>>For Editing Time Schedule<<<<<<
or the website guide: 
https://www.raspberrypi.org/documentation/linux/usage/cron.md
https://www.garron.me/en/linux/run-cronjob-every-5-five-minutes-hours.html

1. Open command prompt or Terminal
2. Type crontab -e
3. Edit the values under
-Water Pump Schedule
-Humidity and Temperature Schedule
-Camera Schedule
4. Save after editing

--Current Settings as of January 27, 2021

-Water Pump Schedule
--Pump1 -Daily 9am, 8 seconds
--Pump2 -Daily 9am, 2 seconds

-Humidity and Temperature Schedule
--Daily, Every hour

-Camera Schedule
--Daily, every 9am and every 5pm

>>>>>>>For Editing Pump Duration Schedule<<<<<<
1. Open Python code on Desktop/gardenpi_files/waterpump.py
2. Edit the parts below:
---pump1_duration = 8
---pump2_duration = 2
Duration is in seconds
3. Save File

>>>>>>>View Activity Logs and Pictures<<<<<<
1. Pump Activity logs are in /home/pi/Desktop/gardenpi_files/pumprecord.txt
2. Humidy and Temperature logs are in /home/pi/Desktop/gardenpi_files/humidityandtemp.txt
3. Pictures are saved in /home/pi/Desktop/gardenpi_files/pictures
4. Picture Logs are in /home/pi/Desktop/gardenpi_files/picturelist.txt